criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient aged 65 or more, living at home;

          -  Presenting a frailty syndrome for the second phase, and robust volunteers for the
             first phase;

          -  Informed and written consent by the patient or the legal representative or the
             reliable person when appropriate.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  No access to ADSL;

          -  Patient's life expectancy less than 12 months;

          -  Patient presenting disability with an Activity of Daily Living score < 4/6 and/or a
             Mini Mental State <24/30;

          -  Non agreement of study participation of patients or legal representative or the
             reliable person when appropriate.
